563: // ServerTransportCredentials builds transport credentials for a gRPC server using the
564: // given properties. If cacertFile is blank, the server will not request client certs
565: // unless requireClientCerts is true. When requireClientCerts is false and cacertFile is
566: // not blank, the server will verify client certs when presented, but will not require
567: // client certs. The serverCertFile and serverKeyFile must both not be blank.
568: func ServerTransportCredentials(cacertFile, serverCertFile, serverKeyFile string, requireClientCerts bool) (credentials.TransportCredentials, error) {
